
== Installation
	
		Install SWTBot via the Eclipse Update manager
		which you find under
		menu:
			<guimenu>Help</guimenu>
			<guisubmenu>Install New Software...</guisubmenu>
		</menuchoice>
		. The update site
		for the
		SWTBot
		is: _http://download.eclipse.org/technology/swtbot/releases/latest/_
	
	
		Install the
		_SWTBot Eclipse Features_
		and the
		_SWTBot SWT Features_
		.
	



